#Options
   • See .vimrc for necessary config options and packages
   • files necessary for syntastic and ycm
      ◦ .ycm_extra_conf.py
         ▸ project specifc flags and directories
         ▸ there is an auto create script that can be used
      ◦ .syntastic_clang_check_config
         ▸ used for custom include directories and other compiler flags
         ▸ can use any name for file and set in .vimrc
         ▸ file is searched for in dir of source files then recursively upwards
